org.openimaj.image.processing.face.detection.keypoints

Class FacialKeypoint

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openimaj.image.processing.face.detection.keypoints.FacialKeypoint
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ReadableBinary, ReadWriteableBinary, WriteableBinary
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    FacePatchFeature.DetectedFacePart

    public class FacialKeypoint
extends Object
implements ReadWriteableBinary
    A FacialKeypoint represents a keypoint on a face. Keypoints are representative points found on all faces.

    Keypoint types are based on Mark Everingham's Oxford VGG Baseline Face Processing Code

    Author:
    Jonathon Hare (jsh2@ecs.soton.ac.uk)
